Requires

   POSIX environment
   Standard POSIX /bin/sh
   curl(1) client

To install (as root)

   install -m 755 ddns-duckdns.sh /usr/local/bin/ddns-duckdns
   mkdir -p ~/.duckdns

   # Copy TOKEN from your account page
   # DOMAIN.duckdns.org

   echo TOKEN > ~/.duckdns/token
   echo DOMAIN > ~/.duckdns/domain
